<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Login Failed</title>
<link
	href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css"
	rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-offwhite-100 text-gray-800">
	<div
		class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-offwhite-200">
		<div class="max-w-md mx-auto p-6 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-dark-blue-900 mb-4">Login
				Failed</h1>
			<p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">We were unable to log you in with
				the provided credentials. This could be due to an incorrect username
				or password, or your account might be inactive. Please ensure your
				login details are correct and try again. If you need further
				assistance, you might need to register as an admin or reattempt the
				login process. Your account's security and accessibility are our top
				priorities, and we aim to provide a seamless experience for all
				users.</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
				<a href="RegisterPage.jsp"
					class="text-center bg-white text-dark-blue-800 py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-dark-blue-700 transition duration-300">Register
					as Admin</a> <a href="LoginPage.jsp"
					class="text-center bg-white text-dark-blue-800 py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-dark-blue-700 transition duration-300">Login
					Using Credentials</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
